{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775843782835,"sessionID":"ses_287781959ffea28iPSNG43jv0n","part":{"id":"prt_d7889103a001095y4S4WT9alI4","messageID":"msg_d7889060b0014awR0E2Hec0QRb","sessionID":"ses_287781959ffea28iPSNG43jv0n","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_7673b3c7216244a3a2f9c78e","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-005 Sandbox 创建处理器 - Verification Report\n\n## Summary\n\n**Status**: ❌ **NOT FULLY COMPLIANT** - Several critical gaps identified\n\n---\n\n## Spec Requirements vs Implementation\n\n### 1. Client-Go Typed Client Interface\n\n**Spec Requirement** (`deployment/client-go.md`):\n```go\ntype AgentRuntimeInterface interface {\n    Create(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.CreateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    Update(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    UpdateStatus(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    Delete(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n    DeleteCollection(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.DeleteOptions, listOpts metav1.ListOptions) error\n    Get(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.GetOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    List(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeList, error)\n    Watch(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (watch.Interface, error)\n    Patch(ctx context.Context, name string, pt types.PatchType, data []byte, opts metav1.PatchOptions, subresources ...string) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    AgentRuntimeExpansion\n}\n```\n\n**Implementation Status**: ✅ **PARTIALLY IMPLEMENTED**\n\nThe implementation uses `dynamic.Interface` instead of typed client:\n- `pkg/workloadmanager/handler/agent_runtime.go:28` - Uses `dynamic.NamespaceableResourceInterface`\n- `pkg/workloadmanager/handler/code_interpreter.go:27` - Uses `dynamic.NamespaceableResourceInterface`\n\n**Gap**: No typed client implementation exists. The code relies on dynamic client which doesn't provide type safety.\n\n---\n\n### 2. Lister Interfaces\n\n**Spec Requirement** (`deployment/client-go.md`):\n```go\ntype AgentRuntimeLister interface {\n    List(selector labels.Selector) ([]*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    AgentRuntimes(namespace string) AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister\n    AgentRuntimeListerExpansion\n}\n\ntype AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister interface {\n    List(selector labels.Selector) ([]*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    Get(name string) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    AgentRuntimeNamespaceListerExpansion\n}\n```\n\n**Implementation Status**: ⚠️ **CUSTOM IMPLEMENTATION**\n\nLocated in `pkg/workloadmanager/processor/sandbox_processor.go:56-67`:\n```go\ntype AgentRuntimeLister interface {\n    AgentRuntimes(namespace string) AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister\n}\n\ntype AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister interface {\n    Get(name string) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n}\n```\n\n**Gap**: \n- Missing `List(selector labels.Selector)` method in both interfaces\n- Missing expansion interfaces (`AgentRuntimeListerExpansion`, `AgentRuntimeNamespaceListerExpansion`)\n\n---\n\n### 3. Informer Types\n\n**Spec Requirement** (`deployment/client-go.md`):\n```go\ntype AgentRuntimeInformer interface {\n    Informer() cache.SharedIndexInformer\n    Lister() runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeLister\n}\n```\n\n**Implementation Status**: ❌ **NOT IMPLEMENTED**\n\n- `pkg/workloadmanager/routes.go:67` references `runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeInformer` which does not exist\n- **Build Error**: `undefined: runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeInformer`\n\n**Gap**: Informer interfaces are referenced but not defined anywhere in the codebase.\n\n---\n\n### 4. REST Resource Plurals\n\n**Spec Requirement** (`deployment/client-go.md`):\n- AgentRuntime: `agentruntimes`\n- CodeInterpreter: `codeinterpreters`\n\n**Implementation Status**: ✅ **CORRECT**\n\n- `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go` should define these (verified via handler usage)\n- `pkg/workloadmanager/handler/agent_runtime.go:28` uses `\"agentruntimes\"`\n- `pkg/workloadmanager/handler/code_interpreter.go:27` uses `\"codeinterpreters\"`\n\n---\n\n### 5. Sandbox Processor Core Functions\n\n**Implementation Status**: ✅ **IMPLEMENTED**\n\nLocated in `pkg/workloadmanager/processor/sandbox_processor.go`:\n\n| Function | Status | Notes |\n|----------|--------|-------|\n| `GenerateSessionID()` | ✅ | Line 109-114 |\n| `BuildSandboxObject()` | ✅ | Line 139-237 |\n| `BuildCodeInterpreterSandbox()` | ✅ | Line 269-320 |\n| `BuildSandboxClaimObject()` | ✅ | Line 239-266 |\n| `CreateSandbox()` | ✅ | Line 383-467 |\n| `resolvePodIP()` | ✅ | Line 322-367 |\n| `rollback()` | ✅ | Line 469-473 |\n\n---\n\n### 6. Sandbox Creation Handler\n\n**Implementation Status**: ✅ **IMPLEMENTED**\n\n| Handler | Endpoint | Status |\n|---------|----------|--------|\n| `HandleAgentRuntimeCreate` | `POST /v1/agent-runtime` | ✅ Line 44-101 |\n| `HandleCodeInterpreterCreate` | `POST /v1/code-interpreter` | ✅ Line 104-164 |\n\n---\n\n## Test Results\n\n### Passing Tests ✅\n- All handler tests (`agent_runtime_test.go`, `code_interpreter_test.go`)\n- All response tests (`response/response_test.go`)\n- Basic processor tests:\n  - `TestRandString`\n  - `TestGetAgentRuntime`\n  - `TestGetCodeInterpreter`\n  - `TestBuildEntryPoints`\n  - `TestResolvePodIP`\n\n### Failing Tests ❌\n- `TestBuildSandboxObject` - **FAILS** (3 assertions fail)\n  - Line 235: session-id label not set correctly\n  - Line 236: app label not set correctly  \n  - Lines 245-246: command/args type mismatch (expected `[]interface{}`, got `[]string`)\n\n- `TestBuildCodeInterpreterSandbox` - **FAILS** (1 assertion fails)\n  - Line 272: session-id label not set correctly\n\n### Build Errors ❌\n```\npkg/workloadmanager/routes.go:67:27: undefined: runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeInformer\npkg/workloadmanager/routes.go:75:27: undefined: runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreterInformer\n```\n\n---\n\n## API Contracts Verification\n\n### Request/Response Format\n\n**CreateSandboxRequest** (`types/sandbox_types.go:9-14`):\n```go\ntype CreateSandboxRequest struct {\n    Kind      string            `json:\"kind\"`\n    Name      string            `json:\"name\"`\n    Namespace string            `json:\"namespace\"`\n    Labels    map[string]string `json:\"labels,omitempty\"`\n}\n```\n✅ Matches usage in handlers\n\n**CreateSandboxResponse** (`types/sandbox_types.go:34-39`):\n```go\ntype CreateSandboxResponse struct {\n    SessionID   string              `json:\"sessionId\"`\n    SandboxID   string              `json:\"sandboxId\"`\n    SandboxName string              `json:\"sandboxName\"`\n    EntryPoints []SandboxEntryPoint `json:\"entryPoints\"`\n}\n```\n✅ Correctly populated by handlers\n\n---\n\n## Critical Issues\n\n### 1. Missing Client-Go Generated Code ❌\nThe spec describes a complete generated client-go library structure, but:\n- No `client-go/` directory exists\n- No typed clients (`AgentRuntimeInterface`, `CodeInterpreterInterface`)\n- No informer factories\n- No lister implementations (only custom interfaces)\n\n### 2. Informer Type References Without Definition ❌\n`routes.go` references undefined informer types causing build failures.\n\n### 3. Test Failures ⚠️\nTwo critical test failures indicate bugs in `BuildSandboxObject` and `BuildCodeInterpreterSandbox`:\n- Labels are not being copied correctly from runtime/interpreter objects\n- Type conversion issues with command/args slices\n\n### 4. Expansion Interfaces Missing ⚠️\nNo expansion interfaces defined for listers (though this is lower priority).\n\n---\n\n## Recommendations\n\n### Immediate (P0)\n1. **Fix build errors**: Either define informer interfaces or remove references in `routes.go`\n2. **Fix test failures**: Debug label copying in `BuildSandboxObject` and `BuildCodeInterpreterSandbox`\n3. **Fix type conversions**: Ensure command/args are converted to `[]interface{}` properly\n\n### Short-term (P1)\n4. **Generate client-go code**: Run `make gen-client` to generate typed clients, informers, and listers\n5. **Add missing lister methods**: Implement `List(selector)` in custom lister interfaces or use generated ones\n\n### Long-term (P2)\n6. **Add expansion interfaces**: Define expansion interfaces for future extensibility\n7. **Add Watch support**: Currently not implemented in handlers\n8. **Add UpdateStatus support**: Required for status subresource updates\n\n---\n\n## Conclusion\n\nThe **core sandbox creation functionality is implemented** (processor, handlers, routes), but the **client-go infrastructure described in the spec is NOT implemented**. The code currently uses dynamic client as a workaround, which works but lacks type safety.\n\n**Compliance Score**: ~60%\n- Core logic: ✅ Implemented\n- Test coverage: ⚠️ Partial (2 failing tests)\n- Client-go spec: ❌ Not implemented\n- Build status: ❌ Failing\n","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/verification-report.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/pkg/workloadmanager/routes.go\">\nERROR [67:27] undefined: runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeInformer\nERROR [75:27] undefined: runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreterInformer\n</diagnostics>","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/pkg/workloadmanager/handler/agent_runtime.go":[{"range":{"start":{"line":122,"character":44},"end":{"line":122,"character":55}},"severity":4,"code":"default","codeDescription":{"href":"https://pkg.go.dev/golang.org/x/tools/go/analysis/passes/modernize#any"},"source":"any","mes